title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week Zero
description:
The boys are back for another season of Pick Em. A season Rico has dubbed as "The Last Dance" We get into all the offseason drama since we've last spoken and write down our goals for the season ahead.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
